<p begin="24020000t" end="39260000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle0">&#x202a;在無垠的黑暗中&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="40370000t" end="73360000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle1">&#x202a;交換革命的誓言&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="74400000t" end="144370000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle2">&#x202a;絕不讓任何人阻撓&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="260590000t" end="303930000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle3">&#x202a;果實宣告了未知的將來&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="304970000t" end="371300000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle4">&#x202a;夢想蛻變成理想&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="415080000t" end="499380000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle5">&#x202a;任誰都渴望落幕…&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="516510000t" end="531750000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle6">&#x202a;在無垠的黑暗中&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="532860000t" end="565510000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle7">&#x202a;交換革命的誓言&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="566560000t" end="618210000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle8">&#x202a;絕不讓任何人阻撓&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="619280000t" end="669220000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle9">&#x202a;總有一天我會讓你看到&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="670330000t" end="733360000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle10">&#x202a;光輝閃耀的世界&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="801800000t" end="831150000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle11">&#x202a;第10話 疑惑&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="929260000t" end="947910000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle12">&#x202a;我還真吃驚啊,流河&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="954950000t" end="984870000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle13">&#x202a;突然說要一起打網球來增進友誼&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="990990000t" end="1006910000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle14">&#x202a;你不方便嗎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1008000000t" end="1017890000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle15">&#x202a;不會&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1019010000t" end="1048930000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle16">&#x202a;你是知道我的實力才這麼說的嗎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1059390000t" end="1076680000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle17">&#x202a;放心吧,夜神&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1083740000t" end="1119010000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle18">&#x202a;我以前得過英國青少年組的冠軍&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1129460000t" end="1150730000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle19">&#x202a;如果問他的國籍是不是英國&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1151810000t" end="1178770000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle20">&#x202a;他會認為我是KIRA才這麼問的&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1179840000t" end="1197470000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle21">&#x202a;算了,就問問看吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1205870000t" end="1221450000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle22">&#x202a;你是英國長大的嗎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1228560000t" end="1256200000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle23">&#x202a;我在那住了5年多&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1257250000t" end="1310610000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle24">&#x202a;請放心吧&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;你絕對無法因此查到L的底細&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1320650000t" end="1329630000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle25">&#x202a;是嗎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1344670000t" end="1378340000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle26">&#x202a;6局先拿下一場的人就算贏囉&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1384380000t" end="1393020000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle27">&#x202a;我知道了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1463120000t" end="1487800000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle28">&#x202a;這只是一場友誼賽&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1495160000t" end="1519500000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle29">&#x202a;無法用來判斷他是否為KIRA&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1538870000t" end="1555820000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle30">&#x202a;但是KIRA很好強&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1642640000t" end="1654240000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle31">&#x202a;15比0了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1672330000t" end="1684270000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle32">&#x202a;喂,流河&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1685350000t" end="1700250000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle33">&#x202a;一上場就玩真的啊&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1706700000t" end="1718300000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle34">&#x202a;先下手為強&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1731390000t" end="1752660000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle35">&#x202a;什麼叫不能說?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1753750000t" end="1767060000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle36">&#x202a;實在很抱歉&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1777440000t" end="1818050000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle37">&#x202a;L指示我們不能對外人洩露&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;即使是次長您也…&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1819150000t" end="1847480000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle38">&#x202a;連問在哪做什麼也都不行?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1853180000t" end="1866830000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle39">&#x202a;實在很抱歉&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1907230000t" end="1922810000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle40">&#x202a;夜神啊&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1923920000t" end="1965220000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle41">&#x202a;KIRA事件曝光之後&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;已經過4個多月了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1971630000t" end="1995630000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle42">&#x202a;社會輿論都在說警方無能&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1996660000t" end="2011330000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle43">&#x202a;說L也無能&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2012340000t" end="2030310000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle44">&#x202a;恕敢直言,次長&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2031360000t" end="2073000000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle45">&#x202a;難道那些害怕KIRA&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;而辭職的警察不無能嗎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2074070000t" end="2119690000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle46">&#x202a;您應該清楚總部裡還剩多少人&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2120780000t" end="2137730000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle47">&#x202a;在意輿論的話&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2138800000t" end="2190110000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle48">&#x202a;就去努力掩飾警員從上到下&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;都害怕KIRA而臨陣脫逃的事實吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2211540000t" end="2221430000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle49">&#x202a;我告辭了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2238900000t" end="2246860000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle50">&#x202a;夜神&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2263590000t" end="2297950000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle51">&#x202a;L如何?能信得過嗎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2311640000t" end="2335300000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle52">&#x202a;我覺得他的能力在我們之上&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2345000000t" end="2376280000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle53">&#x202a;他也冒著生命危險親自調查&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2431760000t" end="2449730000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle54">&#x202a;他們真的是外行人嗎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2450780000t" end="2466020000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle55">&#x202a;他們是誰啊&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2467130000t" end="2492380000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle56">&#x202a;夜神月和流河旱樹&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2493490000t" end="2519770000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle57">&#x202a;是今年入學考雙榜首的兩個人&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2535860000t" end="2550530000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle58">&#x202a;放心吧,夜神&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2551540000t" end="2567120000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle59">&#x202a;雖然說KIRA很好強&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2568230000t" end="2600540000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle60">&#x202a;KIRA以外的人也大多想要獲勝的&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2612270000t" end="2644920000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle61">&#x202a;要是一心想贏就很像KIRA了吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2645970000t" end="2665310000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle62">&#x202a;但故意輸的話&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2666330000t" end="2694310000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle63">&#x202a;會被想成因為怕被當成KIRA&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;而故意輸掉比賽&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2695350000t" end="2728680000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle64">&#x202a;但是這樣反而會有反效果吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2739060000t" end="2752710000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle65">&#x202a;結果都一樣&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2759080000t" end="2788090000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle66">&#x202a;那傢伙並不想用&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;這場球賽來試探什麼&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2794120000t" end="2813460000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle67">&#x202a;這場比賽有其他目的&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2830820000t" end="2843100000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle68">&#x202a;就算是網球比賽…&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2852510000t" end="2862400000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle69">&#x202a;贏的也會是我&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2919910000t" end="2941180000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle70">&#x202a;看吧,果然很想打贏&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2945600000t" end="2971200000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle71">&#x202a;比數4比4&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2987650000t" end="3023260000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle72">&#x202a;什麼時候起連主審和線審都有啦&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3033360000t" end="3040980000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle73">&#x202a;學長&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3050710000t" end="3081310000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle74">&#x202a;我覺得聽過夜神月的名字&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;結果查了之後發現&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3082410000t" end="3111420000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle75">&#x202a;他是』02年和』03年的國中冠軍&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3112440000t" end="3152710000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle76">&#x202a;他在國三的頒獎典禮上說&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;「就玩到初中為止了」&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3153810000t" end="3175080000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle77">&#x202a;之後就再也沒有參加任何大賽了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3194520000t" end="3243210000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle78">&#x202a;那個和他不相上下的&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;流河又是什麼人啊&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3266260000t" end="3303570000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle79">&#x202a;夜神,我瞭解你的想法了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3310970000t" end="3340320000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle80">&#x202a;這場球賽&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;不是用來加深我們的友誼&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3341330000t" end="3377960000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle81">&#x202a;是讓雙方同意&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;彼此的關係早已深厚的儀式&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3391050000t" end="3410960000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle82">&#x202a;透過這場球賽&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3412070000t" end="3454730000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle83">&#x202a;你會認為&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;我已經準備更進一步接近你了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3470460000t" end="3514490000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle84">&#x202a;你是想誘導我說出&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;只有KIRA才知道的事吧&#x202c;</p>
