<p begin="12035020000t" end="12049690000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle346">&#x202a;什麼玩意&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12050700000t" end="12073340000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle347">&#x202a;只能拿出這種企劃嗎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12074390000t" end="12101690000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle348">&#x202a;別以為不管內容是什麼&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12102750000t" end="12132100000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle349">&#x202a;只要是KIRA的就能提高收視率&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12133120000t" end="12163380000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle350">&#x202a;之前我的節目收視率高&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12164480000t" end="12193490000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle351">&#x202a;是因為做了其他人想不到的題材&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12194510000t" end="12205430000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle352">&#x202a;知道嗎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12211530000t" end="12238150000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle353">&#x202a;關鍵在題材,題材&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12239220000t" end="12258220000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle354">&#x202a;快點拿出好的題材來&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12263910000t" end="12276190000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle355">&#x202a;話是沒錯…&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12277260000t" end="12303540000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle356">&#x202a;但是警方都不透露,太難了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12304620000t" end="12312240000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle357">&#x202a;笨蛋&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12313300000t" end="12324560000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle358">&#x202a;要是沒有題材&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12325640000t" end="12348960000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle359">&#x202a;就算亂編也要自己做出來&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12376690000t" end="12402290000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle360">&#x202a;有急件快遞送來&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12411390000t" end="12423670000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle361">&#x202a;這是什麼啊&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12435420000t" end="12447360000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle362">&#x202a;誰寄來的?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12500820000t" end="12549510000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle363">&#x202a;就是這個&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;就是要你們拿出這種東西&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12557210000t" end="12582120000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle364">&#x202a;真讓人興奮啊&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12583230000t" end="12609510000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle365">&#x202a;KIRA要給全世界的訊息&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12610590000t" end="12630500000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle366">&#x202a;如果不照辦的話&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12631610000t" end="12665620000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle367">&#x202a;我就從貴公司社長開始逐一殺死&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12671650000t" end="12689960000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle368">&#x202a;笨蛋才不照辦呢&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12691010000t" end="12724340000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle369">&#x202a;這要是真的,那可是大獨家了喔&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12725370000t" end="12739360000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle370">&#x202a;喂喂&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12740390000t" end="12765300000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle371">&#x202a;我的心已經興奮的枰枰亂跳了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12805120000t" end="12855060000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle372">&#x202a;看見誰都無法看見的夢&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12856170000t" end="12909870000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle373">&#x202a;捨棄所有不需要的事物&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12910890000t" end="12942860000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle374">&#x202a;無法割捨的感情&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12943930000t" end="12998540000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle375">&#x202a;深藏在我的心裡&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12999650000t" end="13063020000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle376">&#x202a;依然處在現實與理想的夾縫中&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="13064050000t" end="13114680000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle377">&#x202a;即使犧牲的伽鎖拴住敢的腳&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="13115760000t" end="13166390000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle378">&#x202a;無法壓抑滿腔的衝動&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="13167480000t" end="13234830000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle379">&#x202a;因為我有一顆強烈追求的心&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="13245560000t" end="13292890000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle380">&#x202a;虛偽恐懼虛飾憂愁&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="13293940000t" end="13349230000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle381">&#x202a;面對各種負面情緒&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="13350330000t" end="13403000000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle382">&#x202a;我也不會弱到被擊垮&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="13404050000t" end="13447740000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle383">&#x202a;不知孤獨為何物Trickster&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="13510490000t" end="13525160000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle384">&#x202a;照現在的情況看來&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="13526170000t" end="13553810000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle385">&#x202a;4天後L就被幹掉的可能性很高&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="13560880000t" end="13583860000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle386">&#x202a;果然神還是站在我這邊的&#x202c;</p>
